---
title: Herby Pan-Seared Chicken with Farro, Tomatoes, and Fresh Mozzarella
description: What do you get when you combine herbes de Provence with mozzarella and tomato? A French and Italian fusion… Fritalian! In all seriousness, we were shocked by how  much we loved this flavor combination for lunch or dinner and have a feeling you will, too.
